ActFarm Income Protection Act
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide amended amounts of federal funding, under statutory authorities, and to enter into amending agreements, on behalf of the Government of Canada, to those previously authorized for Canadian Agricultural Income Stabilization Inventory Transition Initiative, the Cost of Production Benefit, and the AgriInvest Kickstart Programs, to assist agricultural producers in all provinces and territories.
